original: Kinnevik, Mellersta Sv :es Lantbr. A-B, medarb. i Samf. f. hembygdsvård. Skir.: Gang der ältesten Besied-lung Schwedenis (34), Sv :es äldsta bebygg:hist. i geogr.-arkeol. belysn. (37). Resor t. flert. europ. länder samt Egypten o. Mindre Asien. Hobby: arkeologi. GV:sJmt, KV02kl, RNO, RJohO, KFinlVRO, RS :t-AOGM, PatrGM, ProPatrstGM, SM.
translated: Kinnevik, Mellersta Sv :es Lantbr. A-B, employee of the Society for Local Heritage Conservation. Published: "The Development of Sweden's Oldest Settlement" (1934), "Geographical-Archeological Illustration of Sweden's Oldest Settlement History" (1937). Traveled to several European countries as well as Egypt and Asia Minor. Hobby: archaeology. Grand Cross of the Order of the Polar Star, Knight of the Royal Order of the Seraphim (2nd Class), Knight of the Northern Star, Knight of the Order of Vasa, Royal Society of Sciences Honorary Member, Patriotic Society Honorary Grand Master, Pro Patria Honor Grand Master, Silver Medal.
